>\n<br />\n利申 做左Pastry 八年"},{"pid":"bcb5040fc0203adb3a91d2c74a93607cf2c6fce3","tid":121624,"uid":58285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:05:36.000Z","msg":"同路人！我都好想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係真係頂唔順咁長工時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係斷六親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有好似要從低做起，切下野分下野咁，有排都未有得真係煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相信響我依個廢青未捱到去果個位之前已經quit 左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都想知道多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2966e73651b16bd023b9cceee59959691b0505ef","tid":121624,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:44:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有理想好事<br />\n但plan好點行好緊要<br />\nd高級餐廳大廚都揾唔小架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似係</blockquote><br />\n想知可以點入倒一間好餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0bae97a22b5160845bd531ad250b81c910f665","tid":121624,"uid":73356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有理想好事<br />\n但plan好點行好緊要<br />\nd高級餐廳大廚都揾唔小架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似係</blockquote><br />\n想知可以點入倒一間好餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢行只有識人先會易有好工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0766f0c55cd4e2ecd05c661516c456eef9fb52c","tid":121624,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:02:47.000Z","msg":"以前有人介紹去左一間貴價中菜 做學廚<br />\n做左五日太辛苦走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629318826c258292aacb1b5831dd24641018cca0","tid":121624,"uid":58285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"