"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T18:22:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無問題喎<br />\n<br />\n甜品做得叻, 可以做大師傅, 人工好高</blockquote><br />\n我比較想知你指人工好高即係幾多</blockquote><br />\n五皮左右（十五個月糧）<br />\n五星級酒店餅佬 <br />\nOk la 50K</blockquote><br />\nExecutive pastry chef?<br />\nPastry sous chef?<br />\nChef de partie?<br />\n真係有幾多個人做到呢個位<br />\n大把人捱唔琲呢個位就轉行喇"},{"pid":"4ec03086655eb0fd450a6dad0a115449b0bceb06","tid":121624,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:54:53.000Z","msg":"我係一個廚房佬，係呀係咁粗魯<br />\n小心面試問你有冇聽過"},{"pid":"129e03001bee5a55503954cae5c57a3c4f150b95","tid":121624,"uid":20654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T07:08:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係一個廚房佬，係呀係咁粗魯<br />\n小心面試問你有冇聽過</blockquote><br />\n咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80cd67864917d0e19f27ce5f4356861ea8dbe18e","tid":121624,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T07:36:32.000Z","msg":"人工唔低，識個茶餐廳廚房大佬都三萬幾，不過返6日，每日10小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4985371084f0e5ebbf65fa0167d207186ed561f1","tid":121624,"uid":68813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T07:41:33.000Z","msg":"係興趣就去試下，拿一兩年來玩下試下。<br />\n如果唔得咪搵其他工。<br />\n你想下打工既時間有成30-40年，仲要日日都對住自己不喜歡既工作。"},{"pid":"3fffa06be9c43c8a8d6ccc50b4d16dee27073310","tid":121624,"uid":58285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:09:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無問題喎<br />\n<br />\n甜品做得叻, 可以做大師傅, 人工好高</blockquote><br />\n我比較想知你指人工好高即係幾多</blockquote><br />\n五皮左右（十五個月糧）<br />\n五星級酒店餅佬 <br />\nOk la 50K</blockquote><br />\n但係係咪一開始要由低做起定直接做到廚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}